{"word":"Name","slug":"name","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Name</b> Value of a good name<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=20&chapter=22&verse=1'>Pro 22:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=21&chapter=7&verse=1'>Ecc 7:1</a><br/> A new name given to persons who have spiritual adoption:<br/> - General references<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=62&verse=2'>Isa 62:2</a> <br/> - To Abraham<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=17&verse=5'>Gen 17:5</a> <br/> - To Sarah<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=17&verse=15'>Gen 17:15</a> <br/> - To Jacob<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=32&verse=28'>Gen 32:28</a> <br/> - To Paul<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=13&verse=9'>Act 13:9</a> <br/> Intercessional influence of the name of Jesus<br/> <a href='S:Jesus, The Christ, In His Name'>Jesus, The Christ, In His Name</a><br/> Symbolic<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=28&chapter=1&verse=4'>Hos 1:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=28&chapter=1&verse=6'>Hos 1:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=28&chapter=1&verse=9'>Hos 1:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=28&chapter=2&verse=1'>Hos 2:1</a>"}]}